'''索尼α1'''是[[索尼|索尼]]公司的[[索尼α|α系列]]的旗舰级[[全画幅|全画幅]][[无反光镜可换镜头相机|无反相机]]，发布于2021年1月27日。<ref name="pressrelease">{{cite news|last=|first=|date=27 January 2021|title=Sony announces flagship Alpha 1 mirrorless camera with 50MP sensor and 8K video|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/sony_announces_flagship_alpha_1_mirrorless_camera_with_50mp_sensor_and_8k_video-news-47414.php|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=|website=GSMArena.com|publisher=GSMArena|language=en}}</ref>α1与[[Xperia|Xperia Pro]]智能手机一起发布，后者可以作为{{Link-en|高动态范围视频|High-dynamic-range video|HDR}}监视器以及[[5G|5G]]发射器。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dent|first1=Steve|date=27 January 2021|title=Sony's A1 is a $6,500 50MP camera that shoots 30fps bursts and 8K video|url=https://www.engadget.com/sony-a1-full-frame-full-frame-mirrorless-camera-154222241.htmlarchive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=|website=Engadget|language=en-us}}</ref>该相机针对专业摄影师和视频制作者，预计2021年3月开始发售，建议零售价为6500美元。<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|date=27 January 2021|title=The Alpha 1 is Sony’s new flagship camera with monstrous specs and a $6,500 price|work=The Verge|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/26/22250448/sony-alpha-1-camera-announced-specs-price-release-date|access-date=}}</ref>

